{"help": "https://dadosabertos.aneel.gov.br/api/3/action/help_show?name=package_show", "success": true, "result": {"author": "SGT/ANEEL", "author_email": "master.sgt@aneel.gov.br", "creator_user_id": "41156dc5-1418-42dc-9b77-26e8a26604f0", "id": "5a583f3e-1646-4f67-bf0f-69db4203e89e", "isopen": true, "license_id": "odc-odbl", "license_title": "Open Data Commons Open Database License (ODbL)", "license_url": "http://www.opendefinition.org/licenses/odc-odbl", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "metadata_created": "2026-05-27T15:59:47.289669", "metadata_modified": "2026-06-09T10:02:08.565869", "name": "tarifas-distribuidoras-energia-eletrica", "notes": "Apresenta os valores das Tarifas de Energia - TE e das Tarifas de Uso do Sistema de Distribui\u00e7\u00e3o - TUSD, resultantes dos processos de reajustes tarif\u00e1rios das distribuidoras de energia el\u00e9trica. ", "num_resources": 3, "num_tags": 6, "organization": {"id": "e43edce4-1514-4493-8a22-fe11fa98ef9e", "name": "agencia-nacional-de-energia-eletrica", "title": "Ag\u00eancia Nacional de Energia El\u00e9trica", "type": "organization", "description": "A Ag\u00eancia Nacional de Energia El\u00e9trica (ANEEL), autarquia em regime especial vinculada ao Minist\u00e9rio de Minas e Energia, foi criada para regular o setor el\u00e9trico brasileiro, por meio da [Lei n\u00ba 9.427/1996](http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/leis/l9427cons.htm) e do [Decreto n\u00ba 2.335/1997](http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/decreto/d2335.HTM).\r\n\r\nA ANEEL iniciou suas atividades em dezembro de 1997, tendo como principais atribui\u00e7\u00f5es:\r\n\r\n* Regular a gera\u00e7\u00e3o (produ\u00e7\u00e3o), transmiss\u00e3o, distribui\u00e7\u00e3o e comercializa\u00e7\u00e3o de energia el\u00e9trica;\r\n\r\n* Fiscalizar, diretamente ou mediante conv\u00eanios com \u00f3rg\u00e3os estaduais, as concess\u00f5es, as permiss\u00f5es e os servi\u00e7os de energia el\u00e9trica;\r\n* Implementar as pol\u00edticas e diretrizes do governo federal relativas \u00e0 explora\u00e7\u00e3o da energia el\u00e9trica e ao aproveitamento dos potenciais hidr\u00e1ulicos;\r\n* Estabelecer tarifas;\r\n* Dirimir as diverg\u00eancias, na esfera administrativa, entre os agentes e entre esses agentes e os consumidores, e\r\n* Promover as atividades de outorgas de concess\u00e3o, permiss\u00e3o e autoriza\u00e7\u00e3o de empreendimentos e servi\u00e7os de energia el\u00e9trica, por delega\u00e7\u00e3o do Governo Federal.", "image_url": "2026-05-29-130337.442419Aneel.png", "created": "2026-05-27T12:53:06.102274", "is_organization": true, "approval_status": "approved", "state": "active"}, "owner_org": "e43edce4-1514-4493-8a22-fe11fa98ef9e", "private": false, "state": "active", "title": "Tarifas de aplica\u00e7\u00e3o das distribuidoras de energia el\u00e9trica", "type": "dataset", "url": "https://dadosabertos.aneel.gov.br", "version": "1.0", "extras": [{"key": "Categorias no VCGE", "value": "Energia El\u00e9trica"}, {"key": "Cobertura temporal", "value": "2010 em diante"}, {"key": "Frequ\u00eancia de atualiza\u00e7\u00e3o", "value": "Semanal"}], "groups": [{"description": "", "display_name": "Distribui\u00e7\u00e3o", "id": "ea582e9d-e1b9-40b3-a7bb-5d26a7d3e128", "image_display_url": "", "name": "distribuicao", "title": "Distribui\u00e7\u00e3o"}, {"description": "", "display_name": "Tarifas", "id": "744a19e0-6339-4499-9a2c-77af0957984a", "image_display_url": "", "name": "tarifas", "title": "Tarifas"}], "resources": [{"cache_last_updated": null, "cache_url": null, "created": "2022-03-15T19:39:10.094421", "datastore_active": false, "datastore_contains_all_records_of_source_file": false, "description": "", "format": "PDF", "hash": "", "id": "2d3478e0-8aa0-4cd4-81a7-5f8967cd8804", "last_modified": "2022-03-15T20:41:08.254568", "metadata_modified": "2026-05-28T12:46:57.637840", "mimetype": "application/pdf", "mimetype_inner": null, "name": "Dicion\u00e1rio de dados", "package_id": "5a583f3e-1646-4f67-bf0f-69db4203e89e", "pos